5:
...Are you telling me you're unable to
cooperate?
9:
But the knights under my command
have been very vocal about their
disapproval of our continued efforts
to work with the fiends...
11:
That is irrelevant. If you don't already
know, the peace treaty with the
elves and the fiends is well
underway.
13:
You must learn how to work
together, or else our efforts will have
been for naught!
15: I understand this... But the others—
18:
Enough. Us elves will take care of the
land reclamation.
24:
Yes, thank you for your generosity
and understanding!
30:
It's not just the knights that are
upset. The refugees are as well.
33:
Lilith, you know what it means to be
strong. But you also know what it's
like to be weak, don't you?
35:
No one can always be as strong as
they wish they were.
38:
But I decided to believe in the flame
of courage that burns within us all...
42:
That doesn't mean you need to set
fire to all that stands in your way.
45:
Actually... There's something I'd like
you to see.
51:
*chuckle* Ever the popular one, isn't
he?
60:
No need to push. We've still got
plenty left for everyone!
64: Relax. Be careful not to spill any.
74:
WAH! Lilith?! What are you doing
here?
78:
U-uh, don't get the wrong idea! This
is just... a hobby! Er... Kinda?
81:
Sorry, I know this isn't very hero-like,
but... this is who I am. I wanna help
out however I can.
85:
There's no need to apologize. It is I
who was in the wrong.
96:
Lilith? Wait, you shouldn't go running
off on your own!
108: Ah, well. I'll take his place for now.
111:
Heeey! We've still got plenty of food
left, so don't be shy!
128: So you ended up here of all places.
131:
Yes. People from the moderate
faction guided me here.
133:
They also told me what you and
your friends have been up to. You've
done well, Lilith.
149:
Everyone says you took down the
bad guys! Did you really?
153:
Did you... get the person that killed
my mommy too?
165: Eric... is it really you? You're... alive?
181:
Why are you crying? You're
squeezing too hard, Alk...
189: Sorry you had to see that.
191:
Got something in my eyes and
couldn't stop the tears, you know?
No big deal.
193: Just... please keep this between us?
197:
You were right. You really aren't a
hero, but I suppose we have that in
common and more.
210:
Uh, you're not wrong, but... Why bring
it up?
214:
This has served as a reminder of
why I strove to improve myself, and
what I should be doing now.
216:
One day, I'll be the one to pass this
flame to someone else...
220:
...Not sure what you're going on
about, but I'm just glad you seem to
have figured something out.
223:
But for real. Can we keep what just
happened between us?
227:
Of course. It'd be a waste to share
such a secret freely.
